export const USE_AUTHENTICATOR_ERROR = '`useAuthenticator` must be used inside an `Authenticator.Provider`.';
export const COMPONENT_ROUTE_KEYS = [
    'signIn',
    'signUp',
    'forceNewPassword',
    'confirmResetPassword',
    'confirmSignIn',
    'confirmSignUp',
    'confirmVerifyUser',
    'resetPassword',
    'setupTOTP',
    'verifyUser',
];
